snippet.title: 9Lives Arena GDC 2019 Teaser - Cross-Platform 1v1 RPG
snippet.description:
9Lives Arena (9LA) is a competitive online RPG for PC and consoles. 
Pre-order alpha access via our shop online www.9livesarena.com 
1st closed alpha release is due May 2019
Join us on: https://t.me/NineLivesArena
https://discordapp.com/invite/weqNqKJ
https://twitter.com/9livesarena
https://www.facebook.com/9Livesarena/
Instagram: @9livesarena
